com.adobe.xmp.core

Interface XMPSimple

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<XMPNode>, XMPNode

    public interface XMPSimple
extends XMPNode
    A simple property represents a key/value pair and can be seen as a leaf of the tree (if not qualified).
